Recommendations for mitigating such risks typically include additional checks to identify contracts and ensuring they can accept and correctly handle the Ether transferred. Alternatively, safer transfer methods such as `transfer` or Solidity's `send` (though they have been deprecated in favor of `call` due to the limitations on gas stipend) could be considered.

